title: Wings of Diablo MC Box Set
description: The men in the Wings of Diablo MC Club are all about protecting their women, their club and their town! These men are foul-mouthed, bad boys that don't mind fighting for who they love. Which Wing are you gonna love? For those who love possessive, damaged, hot bikers this boxset is for you. No cheating and all HEA!
author: Rae B. Lake
